    "accordion-section-1": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_block_1_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I’m not completely satisfied with my order—can I return it? And what should I do if there is an issue?",
            "content": "<p>We are pleased to offer a full refund within 30 days of your return request. Please visit our Returns Center for further instructions. Once we have received the returned item and approved it, we will process the refund to your original payment method within 5 business days. Please note, if your package is still in transit, we kindly ask that you wait for it to arrive before initiating the return process and receiving a refund.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_1_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can you provide an update on the status of my return?",
            "content": "<p>Once you have completed the returns process through our Returns Centre and sent your package back to our warehouse, your return will be officially underway. After we receive and inspect your return, we will notify you whether it has been accepted or declined. This process may take up to 5 business days from the date your return tracking status shows as Delivered. If approved, please allow up to 5 business days for the refund to be processed back to your original payment method.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_1_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I exchange an item for a different one?",
            "content": "<p>At present, we are unable to offer exchanges. We kindly recommend that you request a return and place a new order for the desired item. Once your return has been received and processed at our warehouse, a refund will be issued to your original payment method.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_1_4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can you help with a damaged item?",
            "content": "<p>We sincerely apologize that you have received a damaged item. Kindly send a photo of the damaged product, along with your details, to <a href=\"mailto:hello@galtsand.us\">hello@galtsand.us</a> and we will be more than happy to assist you in resolving the issue. Please note that items reported as damaged beyond the 30-day return window are unfortunately ineligible for return or refund.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_nDRMMV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if my item is faulty?",
            "content": "<p>Items are considered faulty if they are received damaged or if a manufacturing fault occurs within 3 months of purchase. After this period, items are not regarded as faulty and may be deemed as showing signs of normal wear and tear.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
