    "section_faq_pEgLpg": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_xr3bUH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if my size is out of stock?",
            "content": "<p>If your size is currently out of stock, please feel free to reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@galtsand.com\">hello@galtsand.com</a>, and we will be happy to check when your desired size will be available. Additionally, you can join our waitlist to receive notifications as soon as it's back in stock. We restock items regularly and are committed to offering the sizes you need.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_aVzARX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I know if an item is in stock?",
            "content": "<p>All available items on our website are in stock, unless marked as \"Out of Stock\" or \"On Backorder.\" If an item is out of stock, you can contact us or sign up for notifications to be alerted when it’s back in stock.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_fzRH8a": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How often do you restock items?",
            "content": "<p>We restock our items based on a variety of factors, including the popularity of each product and the availability of materials. While we aim to restock regularly, the timing can vary depending on these factors. To make sure you're the first to know when your desired items are back in stock, we recommend joining our waitlist. You’ll receive notifications as soon as they're available again.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_wxEHjy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will styles be restocked in the same color or style?",
            "content": "<p>While we do restock our most popular items, there may be instances where certain colors or styles are no longer available. We occasionally introduce new colours or limited-edition styles, so if you're interested in a specific look, it's a good idea to join the waitlist to be notified when similar items become available.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_feXrbL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you restock items from past collections?",
            "content": "<p>Due to the exclusive nature of our collections, past styles may not always be restocked. However, we occasionally re-release fan favorites, and reproduce key items from our core collections, or launch new collections inspired by past designs. Be sure to sign up for our email list to stay up-to-date on the latest releases and restocks.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
