          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I create an account?",
            "content": "<p>You can create an account here: www.galtsand.com and enjoy the following benefits:<br/></p><ul><li>Track your orders and review past purchases</li><li>Save your addresses for quicker checkout</li><li>Manage your account details, address book, and email preferences</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "text_LMUgNA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if I need help on my account?",
            "content": "<p>If you need assistance with your account, please feel free to reach out to our customer support team. You can contact us via email at <a href=\"mailto:help@galtsand.us\">hel</a><a href=\"mailto:lo@galtsand.us\">lo@galtsand.us</a> and we will be more than happy to assist you with any account-related queries.<br/></p>"
