    "accordion-section-2": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_block_2_0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "When do you restock sold out items?",
            "content": "<p>We are working diligently to restock our items as soon as possible. In the meantime, please visit the product page and click on <strong>Join The Waitlist</strong> for the item you desire, and you’ll be among the first to be notified when it is back in stock.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_2_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Where is my order?",
            "content": "<p>Once your order is placed, kindly allow three to five business days for it to be packed and shipped from our warehouse. As soon as your order is dispatched, you will receive an email containing your tracking information, so you can monitor your package’s progress online. Please allow up to 7 business days for delivery for orders within the United States, and up to 25 days for international orders from the date your order is shipped.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_2_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "My package is missing, can you help?",
            "content": "<p>We’re truly sorry to hear that your package is missing. Please reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:help@galtsand.us\">hello@galtsand.us</a> with your order details, and we’ll investigate the issue as quickly as possible. We’ll work with you to resolve it and ensure your order gets to you.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_2_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, we are pleased to offer both standard and express shipping options to most countries. For further details on international shipping, including any applicable fees or restrictions, please refer to our shipping policy or contact our customer service team for assistance. We are committed to ensuring a smooth and efficient delivery experience for our international customers.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_block_2_4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "May I change address information on my current order?",
            "content": "<p>Once an order is placed, it begins processing immediately and, regrettably, cannot typically be altered or stopped. However, if your order has already shipped and you need to amend any address details, we recommend contacting the relevant shipping carrier directly. Please bear in mind that making changes to addresses or shipping methods may impact delivery processing times and could incur additional fees, which would be payable directly to the carrier.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_xXQMaa": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will I have to pay import duties on my international order?",
            "content": "<p>Any international order may be subject to import duties and taxes upon arrival, depending on the destination country’s regulations. These charges are the responsibility of the customer and are not included in the price of the order. We recommend checking with your local customs office for further details.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
