    "section_faq_GkdRNA": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_9C9h6J": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How is Galtsand practicing environmental responsibility?",
            "content": "<p>At Galtsand, we are dedicated to making a positive impact on the environment. We aim to use recycled materials wherever possible, ensuring our products are crafted with sustainability in mind. Our manufacturers operate with solar panels to reduce energy consumption, and we continue to explore eco-friendly production methods. We are committed to creating fashion that respects the natural environment, from the materials we use to the way we create each piece, with the goal of reducing our carbon footprint and promoting a more sustainable future.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6KK4R9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are your factory workers paid a fair wage?",
            "content": "<p>At Galtsand, we take pride in our roots in manufacturing and the strong relationships we have built with our partners. Our executive team, with extensive experience in the manufacturing industry, ensures that all warehouse and factory workers are paid fair wages, work in safe environments, and have access to healthy working conditions. We strictly oversee every aspect of our manufacturing operations to guarantee ethical practices, prioritising the well-being of those who help create our products. This commitment to fairness and responsibility is integral to how we do business.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_tHxT3w": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you have an affiliate program?",
            "content": "<p>Our influencer program is currently invite-only. If you’d like to apply, please feel free to reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@galtsand.us\">hello@galtsand.us</a>, and we’ll be happy to review your application.<br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
